						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">noattack wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">So presumably sprite 0 could be part of an active player sprite, moving all over the place, triggering the PPUSTATUS flag -- but ignored since it's not needed.</div><br />Sure, no problem.<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">I can't think of a reason why this would ever be necessary, but are there any instances where sprite 0 is used but its tile index is changed during gameplay?</div>
